## Naming discipline

The task ID in your dispatch prompt is internal addressing — keep it out of the code you ship.
Commit messages, PR titles, and **code comments** describe the change in human terms; never write
`# honour T5 write-only-first` into a committed file. A future reader has no ID decoder.

